    <div class="ed-section-head"><h2>The trip</h2></div>
    <div class="ed-prose">
      <p>Five nights on Lake Hartwell at a brand-new 5,000 sq ft lakefront house near the GA/SC border, about 1.5 hours from Greenville via I-85. Pontoon rental booked for the middle three days. Dock has deep water for swimming and fish bite right off it.</p>
    </div>
