      <dt>Check-in</dt><dd>Monday, July 6 · 4:00 PM</dd>
      <dt>Checkout</dt><dd>Saturday, July 11 · 11:00 AM</dd>
      <dt>Address</dt><dd><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/675+Old+Mill+Road+Hartwell+GA+30643" target="_blank">675 Old Mill Road, Hartwell, GA 30643</a></dd>
      <dt>Listing</dt><dd><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/934751170644664612" target="_blank">View on Airbnb</a></dd>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <!-- The house -->
  <section class="ed-section">
    <div class="ed-section-head"><h2>The house</h2><div class="aside">Serenity Point</div></div>
    <div class="ed-prose">
      <p>5,000 sq ft, brand new. Airbnb Guest Favorite (top 5%). Reviewers call out the stocked kitchen and comfortable beds. Paved walkway from the house to the covered dock so all ages can get down easily.</p>
    </div>
    <dl class="ed-kv" style="margin-top:18px;">
      <dt>Sleeping</dt><dd>6 king bedrooms (4 en suite on main level) + kids' room with 2 bunk beds and a toddler bed. 10 beds across 7 bedrooms.</dd>
      <dt>Bathrooms</dt><dd>5.5</dd>
      <dt>Dock</dt><dd>Covered, deep-water, private boat slip. Swimmable. Fish off it.</dd>
    </dl>
